data.description: RARE FIND - Village builders Madison plan with five bedrooms and four full baths. Primary and one bedroom with full bath on first floor (mother-in-law suite) with game room, formal dining, home office/study and backyard oasis with pool/spa/waterfall and a three car garage! New roof in 2015. Primary bedroom has custom built cabinetry. Backyard oasis has a screened porch, TV mount, fruit trees and the pool was re-plastered in 2020 and new pool decking in 2019. Gourmet kitchen boasts a center island, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and reverse osmosis drinking water. Long Meadow Farms has many amenities, tennis courts, pools, lakes, walking/biking trails and academically recognized Lamar Consolidated ISD. Elementary school is within walking distance.Too many upgrades/updates too mention here, please see attachments.Video/Virtual tour is attached.
